{"id": 2866, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常生活中你都如何给自己花式打圆场的？", "description": "生活不易，需要自我催眠式自洽。（题图来自：视觉中国©️Collection Mix: Subjects）", "record_count": 2130, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190325233851uXiGN4apcMZLRg6F.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-28T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 336129, "content": "来都来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621758}, {"id": 336136, "content": "我长胖也是为了储存胶原蛋白啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126152}, {"id": 336137, "content": "没事，反正一切都会好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498015}, {"id": 336138, "content": "吃亏是福", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185136}, {"id": 336394, "content": "明天我肯定做到\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617388}, {"id": 335628, "content": "打游戏赢了：这把 carry 了；打输了：队友毫无配合。", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336141, "content": "金钱的诱惑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536652}, {"id": 336144, "content": "反正喝水也会pang，那不如喝奶茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621805}, {"id": 337168, "content": "明天在开始减肥，真的是明天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626710}, {"id": 336147, "content": "今晚我要早点睡，先打会儿游戏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621821}, {"id": 336148, "content": "距离上司的提交期限还有时间，我还能再歇会", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621829}, {"id": 338452, "content": "说到做到真的很难", "image": "img/option/option/20190410192306PUtMH1eES7corFOj", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633894}, {"id": 336151, "content": "说好了才可以减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620939}, {"id": 336152, "content": "对哦", "image": "img/option/option/20190328161939tRYvdXELCHOBW2f4", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620939}, {"id": 336153, "content": "再玩十分钟，一定睡🐷🐷🐷", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621848}, {"id": 336155, "content": "明天就不吃了，今天最后一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621851}, {"id": 336159, "content": "今天上了一天课，等明天在背英语吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619609}, {"id": 336161, "content": "。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486582}, {"id": 336163, "content": "睡睡，必须早睡，早睡早起不会老", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736391}, {"id": 336164, "content": "现在都高二下学期，想着等高三就好好学习一定可以考到自己想去的大学", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621878}, {"id": 336166, "content": "不吃东西会低血糖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621894}, {"id": 336167, "content": "本来定的明天去玩，算了，换一下，今天先玩，然后明天也在玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305728}, {"id": 336168, "content": "明天就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602930}, {"id": 336170, "content": "每次干活就算平均数。\n今天玩一天，后面每天也只是多做一点点，没事的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565854}, {"id": 336171, "content": "一定是幻觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617047}, {"id": 336172, "content": "明天晚上一定要开始看书学习。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1436141}, {"id": 336173, "content": "明天会更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615697}, {"id": 336174, "content": "我的肉都是借来的，不是我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599876}, {"id": 336686, "content": "嗯 明天早点起来 锻炼身体 读书 学习 清理屋子 把不要的东西都扔了！第二天：还是睡觉好啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408904}, {"id": 336175, "content": "书摆了好久还没看，我告诉自己，它们还不想见我，我不能强求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621958}, {"id": 336176, "content": "明天再做吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373920}, {"id": 336178, "content": "从未圆过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460843}, {"id": 336182, "content": "提前一个月看机票，嗯，挺便宜，不着急。提前一个星期看，啊，涨价啦，行程该订了。嗯，买了，啊，贵好多。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621969}, {"id": 336183, "content": "明天会更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1587165}, {"id": 336442, "content": "撸会儿猫我就去洗澡 撸着撸着猫睡了\n算了算了 我也一起睡觉得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622718}, {"id": 336955, "content": "没事，别人都是这么过的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625656}, {"id": 336700, "content": "玩完这局就去学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591860}, {"id": 336193, "content": "妈的，又智障了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476280}, {"id": 336449, "content": "好不容易学习了会，不行，等会要多吃点。\n哇，第一次赚到钱了，等会买点好吃的奖励自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622744}, {"id": 336198, "content": "人活着不就是图个开心吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618793}, {"id": 336455, "content": "反正大家最后都会死？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195214}, {"id": 339530, "content": "我要去做一件事！先做另一件事吧，就做一会儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627748}, {"id": 336462, "content": "明天早上起来去吃早饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622159}, {"id": 338256, "content": "花钱使我快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057388}, {"id": 336225, "content": "大雨滂沱没有伞，奔跑起来，总会雨过天晴，没准还能看见彩虹。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622000}, {"id": 335461, "content": "花大价钱买的化妆品管用就说是好用买到了；没效果就怪自己最近熬夜太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336229, "content": "今天一定要把任务做完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621143}, {"id": 335462, "content": "还是明天早起洗头更精神；第二天：容易感冒，还是戴帽子好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336231, "content": "(,,千₃ 千,,)边说边想，\n基本没输过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620496}, {"id": 336232, "content": "游戏打输了，再打一局赢回来；打赢了，再打一局让快乐延续", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1149650}]}